phrases: Oh, so you have an older brother?
He is married and even has a kid.
So I do not see him often.
It is got to be her.
So there were this many people who were watching me.
I heard it is her older brother's child.
You are only in middle school!
What are you going to do about school?
I will skip for a while.
I have been exiled from my house.
The access count is through the roof.
So you will have custody for a while?
I just called my brother, and he sounded like he is fed up.
I only lent it to you because you wanted to wear one so badly.
Besides, did not you see what happened out there?
You will get more customers if I am here.
After all, I am the famous net idol.
Guys are so easy to get.
Oh yeah, I should upload the pictures to my blog.
Only the staff's allowed to wear that uniform.
What, is not it ok if it is just for a little while?
Someone might think we are renting the costume out.
I heard other places do things like that.
I know I am wearing it better than those boring girls out on the street.
Yup, you are cuter than I am.
But you have to give up on taking the photo.
Make sure you take the uniform off, Aoi-chan.
It is Aoi-chan in maid uniform.
No, she is the Chief's niece.
I told her to change, but...
Who is that man that is just dripping with pheromones?
I bet it would feel good to make a guy that good looking worship me.
They are not quite at that stage...
The evening shift kitchen staff cannot show up!
I am hands full with taking care of Aoi-chan!
Why does this have to happen now, of all times?
Do not scare me like that.
A boring woman like that cannot possibly be with him.
I am calling around to find a person that can come in as a substitute, but no luck so far!
We do not have the kitchen staff when we are about to enter peak hours!
We cannot let non-staff work all of a sudden.
However, only if you pass the test.
We will judge you with the omelet rice.
Here are the ingredients and the recipe.
You are really good at cooking.
I would like to eat some, too.
Sure, if you place an order.
Aoi-chan, he is not human, so be careful.
But that is part of what I like about you.
Do not touch me so casually!
It is Aoi-chan the net idol!
Proves how you are a closet otaku, Ikkun.
Since she is a net idol, does she put up swimsuit pictures and such?
Porn's your favorite thing, is not it, Kurotatsu?
But she sometimes posts a picture with a cheeky face, and that is so...
Will not you work as a substitute today?
Then would you like to share a table with me?
Maybe I will go up the stairs once in a while...
There is a limit to how little interest he can show.
All he cares about is that boring woman.
Misa-chan, you can leave it there.
Chief's out of the shop right now.
Why should I care about that?
She should be back soon, so why not sit and wait for a while?
All right, then I will leave you alone.
Hey, there is something I want to ask.
I did not know you were changing.
There is not the slightest hint of femininity!
You are a girl, are not you?!
Besides, are these even a woman's clothes?
Are you trying to dress cutely at all?
I do not get hung up over things like that.
How did you seduce Usui Takumi?!
You must have some kind of secret technique!
There has to be a reason for him to not look at someone as cute as I!
If I make him mine, I will be even cuter than before!
Yet he will not even look at me, and I cannot accept that!
Are you going to let me have your omelet rice?
What do you want me to do?
I want you to be mine, and only mine.
Do you really understand what that means?
Why are you going so far, acting as if this was some kind of contest?!
Everyone knows that you are cute without doing something like this!
If I could get a lot of people to acknowledge that I am cute,
then I thought that I could impress those that laughed at me.
If you want to impress them, then face them straight on!
You cannot fight alone without dragging others in, can you?
I do not know what you had to go through, but I am sure those people that laughed at you in the past will respect you.
Even if you are a boy.
Sorry I never told you all.
He gets really upset if I tell the truth.
You knew it from the start, did not you?
No wonder he never looked at me.
Then why were you on top of him?
I was only facing him straight on, like you did.
Why are not they more surprised?
I am a guy, yet I like cute clothes, and I even cross dress.
Is not it normal to laugh at me, or at least be shocked?
Sure, I was surprised when I figured it out.
But the clothes looked good on you.
How about you go home now?
Next time I come, I will perfect it and make everyone my slave.
You went back to square one...
He even left with a cliche line.
Everything I said was for nothing.
I am here only for Misa-chan.
Masters, is not it about time you leave?
What a cute male middle school student you are!
I am wearing the uniform since I did not have anything else to wear today.
Do not have anything else to wear?
Satsuki-san, could you give me your old clothes again?
So my brother threw them away again.
So Aoi-chan's clothes used to be the Chief's.
I am arranging them and fixing the sizes, too.
It is economical, too, so it is great.
You are wearing something like that again...
You still do not realize how much of a waste it is?
A pink one piece camisole, a mini piece dress with ribbon, and a chiffon top with open shoulders coordinated with a fluffy balloon skirt.
Everyone would admit they look good.
Yet, why do not you show any interest at all?!
You are born as a girl!
You are supposed to look good in clothes made for girls!
Yet your lack of fashion sense and dedication is killing you and it annoys the heck out of me!
I am getting insulted and lectured at the same time.
I will help pick out clothes that will look good on you.
No, there is no way I would look good in anything.
Besides, I do not have any money to buy clothes.
I was just out of notebooks.
We are having a time sale right now.
I will even give you a bigger discount!
I give up on reforming you.
Looks like you did go to school today.
It is suffocating to be at home.
Not like it is any different at school.
Because everyone denies what I like.
It is ridiculous that I should not like them just because I am a guy.
That is why I hate everyone.
I cannot come to like anyone.
If you ask me, I like you.
It is refreshing to watch you.
Are you a masochist while having such a sadist face?
Just so you know, I am not interested in that kind of thing.
Aoi-chan, you are being too loud.
Oh man, the weather forecast is never right.
Aoi-chan, you do not have anything with you to dry yourself off?
I do, but I do not want to use it.
It is my favorite cute handkerchief.
Then I will dry you with my handkerchief.
What does she think she is doing?
If you will not stop, I will use force!
You are crazy to challenge an adult man!
Or am I too masculine for a girl?
I am just like this, so if I made you worry, I will apologize.
People yell at me a lot and tell me to act more feminine.
But I believe it is best to be the way I am.
Even so, I do not accept girls who do not put effort into becoming a good woman.
If you do not polish yourself, you will eventually get dumped and cry over it.
But he sees you as more than just friends.
He is just toying with me and having fun.
He is an alien so you know.
I sympathize with him a little right now.
That is what you get for buying something cheap.
You have got great style, so I am saying I will help you out.
This does not feel quite right...
Should I organize a Lolita day?
Sorry for being a miserable failure when it comes to cuteness.
If you are blushing like that, you look even cuter, and that turns me on.
It is tiring to wear clothes I am not used to.
Hey, were not you all taking pictures of me?
I took so many that the memory filled up.
I picked out her clothes, after all.
She looked really good, did not she?
The paperwork for the district government got piled up.
I have my next part time job to go to.
Ah, please do not worry, Subaru-san.
